  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个数据交换的时序图，场景是消费者端和提供者端通过连接器进行数据共享。主要参与者有四个：ConsumerBackend、ConsumerConnector、ProviderConnector和ProviderBackend。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerBackend",
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "ProviderBackend"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先确认一下顺序。从左到右应该是：ConsumerBackend、ConsumerConnector、ProviderConnector、ProviderBackend，这样符合数据从消费者流向提供者的逻辑吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerBackend",
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "ProviderBackend"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个顺序。接下来第一步是ConsumerConnector向ProviderConnector发起查询，获取可用的data offers。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "query data offers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经画出了ConsumerConnector到ProviderConnector的query data offers消息，然后ProviderConnector返回metadata给ConsumerConnector。接下来呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "query data offers",
        "return metadata"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "返回metadata之后，ConsumerConnector需要发起contract request，然后ProviderConnector回复contract agreement，完成合约协商。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "contract request",
        "contract agreement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "合约协商部分已添加。下一步是获取数据吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "contract request",
        "contract agreement"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，ConsumerConnector发送request artifact，ProviderConnector返回access information。这里有个分支逻辑：数据传输有两种协议，PULL和PUSH，需要用alt框表示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ConsumerConnector",
        "ProviderConnector",
        "request artifact",
        "return access information",
        "alt",
        "protocol.PULL",
        "protocol.PUSH"
