      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "PULL是ConsumerBackend请求数据，ProviderBackend返回。PUSH是ProviderBackend主动推送给ConsumerBackend，然后ConsumerBackend本地处理数据。",
